vices? With emphasis on goals and approaches over tactics or technologies, this enormously popular book gives you knowledge about information architecture with a framework that allows you to learn new approaches -- and unlearn outmoded ones.', DEFAULT, DEFAULT, '528', '2006-11-27', '3', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=2d2Ry2hZc2MC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', 'Information Architecture for the World Wide Web')ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
