ves is a one-stop resource for women of all generations.', DEFAULT, '20.99', '848', '2011-10-04', DEFAULT, 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=kCkc2HIzKhYC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', 'Our Bodies, Ourselves')ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
