/books/content?id=R7C4BgAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', 'MANAGEMENT INFORMATION SYSTEMS IN THE KNOWLEDGE ECONOMY')ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
